{"tid":2174909,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"【玩物達人】砌高達熱血片點擊百萬 職業模型師 創作．攞獎．生活","createTime":"2020-08-26T07:45:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-26T08:25:09.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e717810a43900717137f485d9bf91395c748e5c7","tid":2174909,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T07:45:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/lifestyle/20200826/6DSSXVQ7LREGTACVQCTHUI3H5M/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2F20200826%2F6DSSXVQ7LREGTACVQCTHUI3H5M%2F&d=mfTbPTXtdXcWugdQC%2B6BDiRJil42CLA7NmQUB0MJ4tY%3D&h=36192c2d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2F20200826%2F6DSSXVQ7LREGTACVQCTHUI3H5M%2F&h=5b2e169a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/lifestyle/20200826/6DSSXVQ7LREGTACVQCTHUI3H5M/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n【玩物達人】砌高達熱血片點擊百萬 職業模型師 創作．攞獎．生活<br />\n<br />\n不知道是否因為武肺肆虐，大家多了時間在家，高達模型近來十分搶手，受歡迎的款式往往賣斷市。記者也多了在YouTube看模型片，留意到一條叫做「N Maker」的頻道，影片中精心製作的模型配合專業級的拍片手法，除了靚，還很熱血勵志。唔係誇張，不少影片都有過10萬view數，其中2016年的「鐵血之孤兒」一片更過130萬。我們找來影片製作者、模型師熊沛文（Adam），傾傾模型經，分享砌模型和拍模型片的心得。<br />\n<br />\n「我覺得砌模型，除了完成品，製作過程都好值得去注視和欣賞。」不需要懂得砌模型，看Adam的片你也能感受到每個細節的美感。看着一款模型由簡單的素組（未作上色加工的組裝），經過打磨、刻線、上色等工序後改頭換面，變成屬於個人創作的作品。<br />\n<br />\n以影片「RG EVA-01」為例，如果只看最後製成品，可能會忽略了作為配角、倒在。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\nAdam是全職模型師，主要做模型代工和開模型班教人砌模型。部份影片的主角是做給客人的作品，。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/IqsVHukacdKXye2-wQ4LMEv5LzQ=/6660x4440/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/BW4Q36VBFFCSVMBCHBLO7YAVTI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FIqsVHukacdKXye2-wQ4LMEv5LzQ%3D%2F6660x4440%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FBW4Q36VBFFCSVMBCHBLO7YAVTI.jpg&h=d9c433ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nAdam是全職模型師，五年前開設模型工作室「N Maker」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Ne5FaaQvwI7TW2QS9dUBXKEbRNg=/1920x1080/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/2QC65HHZINBYFHYWZUG5PU6H7Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FNe5FaaQvwI7TW2QS9dUBXKEbRNg%3D%2F1920x1080%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F2QC65HHZINBYFHYWZUG5PU6H7Y.jpg&h=c9cf84e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n工作室也會用作模型教室之用。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/bgrqp31_D7sP1JXNhZOGZtW4OZQ=/6660x4440/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/CMN75H3NLVAGXAOPRIYKYTDOQU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fbgrqp31_D7sP1JXNhZOGZtW4OZQ%3D%2F6660x4440%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FCMN75H3NLVAGXAOPRIYKYTDOQU.jpg&h=9504be93&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nAdam指攝影也是他的嗜好，但之前沒有拍片工作的經驗。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/pQ0nOp_Hm7V_iKEa7mtAQyEFDUc=/6660x4440/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/RGUTETRYRBEZ5G5HLNDWASNGBU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FpQ0nOp_Hm7V_iKEa7mtAQyEFDUc%3D%2F6660x4440%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FRGUTETRYRBEZ5G5HLNDWASNGBU.jpg&h=03dd9d99&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n模型創作不但只有組裝，例如刻線的設計也是模型師個人的創作，每個人不同。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/FOxeoRO3xLZDv2Iz-Hdw_kT51KI=/6660x4440/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ASA2S2KCHVGAPCF276EPKRAS7U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FFOxeoRO3xLZDv2Iz-Hdw_kT51KI%3D%2F6660x4440%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FASA2S2KCHVGAPCF276EPKRAS7U.jpg&h=09d0e9bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n實體書買少見少，Adam是模型雜誌GHL的支持者，他說模型書是模型迷學習的好媒介。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n凡人集結 英雄退場<br />\n<br />\n對於記者這些入門玩家，Bandai點出就點砌，就算上色也是跟官方建議照做，但當你看到Adam等模型高手的作品和心機，也會承認模型是一種創作，可以表達創作者的心境。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n2019年參賽作品《出發》，他直言是受到社會運動影響，「我沒有甚麼可以做，所以將情感放在作品上。」作品有一台巨型高達和一個正在走上駕駛艙的駕駛員，。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n也有網民批評砌模型不應扯上政治，Adam卻認為創作就是將自己的想法和作品連繫，「在那個時間，你的想法牽涉到那個。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/s97WYIT2ICvDuLjCx250DLwrcxg=/4472x6708/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/NFN4N34HZBB6TIPZNQ5FUMJU5U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fs97WYIT2ICvDuLjCx250DLwrcxg%3D%2F4472x6708%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FNFN4N34HZBB6TIPZNQ5FUMJU5U.jpg&h=b9fefd79&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2019年GBWC的作品《出發》。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/NWz6SovcmYTiFxpbQPKKdRIZBK8=/6708x4472/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/LUTDWAUF7ZGYZARTOV37YOVNGA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FNWz6SovcmYTiFxpbQPKKdRIZBK8%3D%2F6708x4472%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FLUTDWAUF7ZGYZARTOV37YOVNGA.jpg&h=bec570ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n駕駛艙的小人才是重點，寓意每一個平凡人的改變比英雄更加重要。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/UOOzO1V_kQDr78Wya6aTs_MkxFw=/4440x6660/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/LWRGKOSKAFDZ7LMH42D65GG7XE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FUOOzO1V_kQDr78Wya6aTs_MkxFw%3D%2F4440x6660%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FLWRGKOSKAFDZ7LMH42D65GG7XE.jpg&h=34f39ac4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nGBWC 2017香港區公開賽第三名，Adam將其命名為「不要死，活下去」，靈感來自《鐵血的孤兒》的劇情和所有為生活努力的人。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/be-cgVcKFggDTkUGF3U_fCtWCtI=/1893x843/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/CAYFYWGDONHNBCMF2P6OVFLS5Y.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fbe-cgVcKFggDTkUGF3U_fCtWCtI%3D%2F1893x843%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FCAYFYWGDONHNBCMF2P6OVFLS5Y.png&h=e371a035&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n技術未足 眼界要夠<br />\n<br />\n或者大家會覺得Adam很有藝術家脾氣，他的創業過程也的確和其他藝術人相若。大學畢業後從事圖像設計工作，覺得工作和。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n想法率性，但實行起來，當模型師的工作和砌模型一樣也需要紀律。「任何事情當它變成工作時，都需要工廠大媽式。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n這樣忙碌，還要額外拍片，想到也覺得累，但Adam覺得有追求就不會厭倦，「模型世界好大，可以追求不同的層面，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n記者：司徒港燊<br />\n<br />\n攝影：潘志恆、伍慶泉"},{"pid":"a7419543822a43a256008e5b113ed4b18816da90","tid":2174909,"uid":3067,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T07:46:59.000Z","msg":"鐵血果張相 好震撼"},{"pid":"3b595cc14a49eabbc30e84b84f44d5ed74d35fba","tid":2174909,"uid":14652,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"a7419543822a43a256008e5b113ed4b18816da90","tid":2174909,"uid":3067,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T07:46:59.000Z","msg":"鐵血果張相 好震撼"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T08:25:09.000Z","msg":"靚係靚，不過果6隻字好撚中二病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}